    "Alignment ensures that the LLM's responses adhere to ethical standards and user-specific requirements, preventing scenarios where the model's behavior diverges from human values or produces harm 1.",
    "Effective alignment strategies involve technical measures, such as adjusting model parameters and training data, and policy measures, such as incorporating feedback loops that allow users to report and rectify misaligned behavior.",
